				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: New Patch message, remove if not needed anymore :)<a name="26759"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 10 04 2:10 PM</span></td>
